## Output Structure

Results will be organized in the following directories:

- `Output/`: Main output directory
  - `Aligned/`: BAM files
  - `VCF/`: Variant calls
  - `Reports/`: Quality reports
  - `Frequencies/`: Allele frequencies
  - `Trimmed/`: Trimmed FASTQ files
  - `Unpaired/`: Unpaired FASTQ files

